198
00:12:47,057 --> 00:12:47,933
Hey,

199
00:12:49,268 --> 00:12:51,103
Merry Christmas.

200
00:12:52,730 --> 00:12:54,106
What is it?

201
00:12:56,817 --> 00:12:58,235
Thank you.

202
00:13:09,538 --> 00:13:10,873
Wow.

203
