245
00:16:10,636 --> 00:16:11,720
- I'm not in a rush.
- Okay.

246
00:16:11,804 --> 00:16:13,889
- I'll be off now.
- Bye.

247
00:17:28,630 --> 00:17:30,549
It's still early, but can I have a drink?

248
00:17:31,050 --> 00:17:33,469
It's something you can't talk about
